If she had seen me,
she would've thought the same

765
00:56:36,936 --> 00:56:38,729
since you were next to me, right?

766
00:56:45,986 --> 00:56:47,446
Your photo…

767
00:56:48,864 --> 00:56:51,158
This memory is enough for me.

768
00:56:51,242 --> 00:56:52,993
