777
00:57:23,858 --> 00:57:26,068
because I've already settled in your home.

778
00:57:33,284 --> 00:57:34,368
In that case,

779
00:57:35,327 --> 00:57:37,079
since it's raining a lot outside…

780
00:57:39,915 --> 00:57:42,042
and to see if we've adapted or not…

781
00:57:48,007 --> 00:57:49,884
Do you want to stay the night here?

782
00:58:00,269 --> 00:58:01,270
With me?

