789
01:02:50,309 --> 01:02:52,019
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">The rejected cases have been resolved!</font></i>

790
01:02:52,102 --> 01:02:53,729
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Don't get too excited just yet.</font></i>

791
01:02:53,812 --> 01:02:56,607
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">If we don't resolve this,</font></i>
