795
01:03:04,114 --> 01:03:06,909
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">There's a place</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">that can rekindle your love.</font></i>

796
01:03:06,992 --> 01:03:08,827
{\an8}I'm going back to Singapore.

797
01:03:08,911 --> 01:03:10,579
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">You haven't told her yet?</font></i>

798
01:03:10,662 --> 01:03:12,748
{\an8}Do you enjoy making a fool out of me?

799
01:03:12,831 --> 01:03:14,166
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Can I ask you something?</font></i>

800
01:03:14,249 --> 01:03:16,084
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">What was your question</font></i>
